  <brief_title>Comparative Evaluation of Results of Allogeneic Hematopoietic Stem Cells Versus Ponatinib in CML Patients Carrying a Mutation T315I</brief_title>
  <official_title>Overall Survival With Ponatinib Versus Allogeneic Stem Cell Transplant in Philadelphia-positive Leukemias With the T315I Mutation</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Hospices Civils de Lyon</agency>
